            "type": "text",
            "text": "You may have noticed Wooden and Stone tools won't cut it anymore. They have 2 durability and don't have any harvest levels. There's a few other materials that don't work either.<br> <br>The first tools that you can make are from Tinker's Construct, using Wood and Flint parts. Or Bone if you're a GTNH player at heart."
