            "text": "The materials in Tinker's Construct have been heavily tweaked as well. I recommend checking Materials & You if you're unsure.<br> <br>You can also use exclusively vanilla-style tools starting from your first Iron, but I do recommend looking into Tinker's Construct. It's more powerful than it might look."
